{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the ","type":"text"},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590"},"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"title":"showsUserLocation","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/showsUserLocation":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","kind":"symbol","title":"showsUserLocation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier"